    "text": "it depends on what you are testing really. For example I have an integration test to make sure that if I hit the network my local SQLite cache saves the items of the responce correctly. For that integration test I mock the network (mockwebserver, normal stub, whatever) but I use the real db because I want to make sure that everything was saved correctly. You can use robolectric for that but I don't trust it",
